  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who were planned for reconstruction of anterior crucial ligament,
             reconstruction of medial patellofemoral ligament and Elmslie-Trillat procedure for
             patella instability.

          -  Patients with synovectomies and menisci resection lasting more than 25 minutes.

          -  Patients &gt; 18 years

          -  Acceptance of informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with rheumatoid arthritis

          -  Patients with a Body Mass index of &gt; 35

          -  Patients who can not read and understand Danish

          -  Fertile women who does not use secure contraception
      </textblock>
